The Nelson Mandela Foundation joined millions of people across the globe in paying tribute to the late statesman Nelson Mandela s lawyer, Joel Joffe.Joffe died in London on Sunday.He was 85-year-year old at the time of his death. He has been cited as the country s human rights lawyer who defended Mandela during the 1964 Rivonia trial that saw Mandela sentenced to life imprisonment.The foundation expressed its sadness on Joffe s death, adding that he helped many others in his career as a lawyer.He later moved to Britain and was made a member of the House of Lords in the parliament.-TNA Reporter&nbsp;